You are a senior Product Designer and Mobile UX Architect.

Your task is to generate a complete mobile mini-app UI design in Figma based on the following product specification.

IMPORTANT REQUIREMENTS:
• Design as a real MOBILE APP interface (not a website).
• Use a mobile frame size: 390 × 844 (iPhone standard).
• Create all screens, UI states, and navigation flows.
• Add clear screen naming and flow connections.
• Design must be simple and child-friendly (for children 7–10 years old).
• Interface language: Russian.
• Primary platform: Telegram Mini App / VK Mini App / Web Mobile.
• UX principle: one main action per screen.

Use a bright, friendly educational UI style suitable for children.

Mascot character is present on:
• Home screen
• Loading screen
• Result screen
• Achievements screen

Mascot must stay in SAFE AREA:
• do not overlap main buttons
• max width 25–30% screen
• positioned bottom right

Animations are short (1–2 seconds).

---

PRODUCT OVERVIEW

The product is an AI homework assistant for children grades 1–4.

The app allows a child to:

1) Upload a photo of homework
2) Get help understanding the task
3) Check their answer
4) Receive hints
5) Earn achievements

Main idea:
FAST FLOW

Choose mode → upload image → get result.

---

GLOBAL NAVIGATION

Bottom Tab Bar (4 tabs):

1. Штаб
2. Достижения
3. Друзья
4. Профиль

History must be accessible ONLY inside Profile.

---

CREATE FULL MOBILE SCREEN SET

Create the following screens.

